{Cite book|last=Thomas|first=Steven D.|authorlink=Steve Thomas (television)|year=1987|title=The Last Navigator|location=New York|pages=|publisher=Henry Holt and Company|isbn=0-8050-0096-8|ref=harv|url=https://archive.org/details/lastnavigator00thom}}\n*{{Cite web|last1=Thomas|first1=Steve|last2=Goodenough|first2=Ward H.|date=|year=1997|url=http://www.penn.museum/sites/Navigation/keeping/keeping.html|work=Keeping Track|title=Traditional Navigation in the Western Pacific|publisher=[[University of Pennsylvania Museum of Archaeology and Anthropology]]|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite web|last=Thompson|first=Nainoa|authorlink=Nainoa Thompson|title=The Wayfinder: The 1980 Voyage Home|url=http://www.pvs-hawaii.com/newsletters/nl_wayfinder.htm|work=An Ocean in Mind|publisher=Polynesian Voyaging Society|accessdate=2010-09-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210060433/http://www.pvs-hawaii.com/newsletters/nl_wayfinder.htm|url-status=live|archivedate=2010-12-10|date=|year=1987|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite web|last=Thompson|first=Nainoa|date=|year=2007|url=http://pvs.kcc.hawaii.edu/holokai/2007/mau_1_intro.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518024159/http://pvs.kcc.hawaii.edu/holokai/2007/mau_1_intro.html|url-status=live|archivedate=2011-05-18|access-date=|title=K\u016b Holo Mau: 2007 Voyage for Mau|website=|publisher=[[Polynesian Voyaging Society]]|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite web|last=Thompson|first=Nainoa|date=|year=2010|url=http://pvs.kcc.hawaii.edu/holokai/1985_1987/nainoa.html|work=Voyage of Rediscovery: 1985-1987|title=Recollections|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518042150/http://pvs.kcc.hawaii.edu/holokai/1985_1987/nainoa.html|url-status=live|archivedate=2011-05-18|publisher=Polynesian Voyaging Society|accessdate=2010-07-29|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite web|last=Thompson|first=Nainoa|date=|year=2010b|title=On Wayfinding|url=http://pvs.kcc.hawaii.edu/ike/hookele/on_wayfinding.html|website=|publisher=Polynesian Voyaging